OL,3,CNew health boss wants to leave Jersey
OL,4,Cwith a 'world-class health service'
OL,6,FChair of the Health and Community
OL,7,FServices Advisory Board has explained
OL,8,Fhis plans to improve the health system.
OL,10,FTom Hayhoe was appointed on 28
OL,11,FFebruary by the island's Health
OL,12,FMinister, Deputy Tom Binet.
OL,14,FMr Hayhoe has stated that one of his
OL,15,Fpriorities is to ensure taxpayers'
OL,16,Fmoney is used efficiently.JIt comes
OL,17,Fafter a health board meeting on last
OL,18,Fmonth revealed that the department is
OL,19,Ffacing a deficit of #32.5 million.
