OL,3,CNew health boss wants to leave Jersey
OL,4,Cwith a 'world-class health service'
OL,6,F"A system that is transparent and has
OL,7,Fpeople listening to them and is there
OL,8,Ffor them."
OL,10,FHe says his background in consumer
OL,11,Frepresentation will be beneficial: "I
OL,12,Fam keen that we listen to the consumer
OL,13,Fof health care, so the patient and the
OL,14,Fservice user and we deliver to them
OL,15,Fwhat they are looking for."
