OL,3,CNew health boss wants to leave Jersey
OL,4,Cwith a 'world-class health service'
OL,6,FIn doing so, Mr Hayhoe wants to ensure
OL,7,Fthe health board are hearing the
OL,8,Fpatients' voices: "We are introducing
OL,9,Fat the beginning of every board
OL,10,Fmeeting half an hour session where we
OL,11,Fwill hear a patient or carer story."
OL,13,FHe adds: "What I want to do is reach
OL,14,Fout to the wider community across the
OL,15,Fisland, different demographics across
OL,16,Fthe island.
